There is possibility to use named queries from [spring data jpa][1].


     &lt;named-query name=&quot;MyData.ultimateFind&quot;&gt;
        &lt;query&gt;select d from MyData d where d.column3 = ?1&lt;/query&gt;
     &lt;/named-query&gt;

